project.title: Ashantis Jones
project.description: Ashantis is an event planner from Cleaveland that entertains and creates memorable events through detail oriented design and calculated execution. Adam designed Ashantis's portfolio to assist in her job hunt as a graduate of the BFA Theatre Management at DePaul University looking for opportunities in the event management space.
